                With multiple releases, powerful music videos, and countless intense shows under their belt, the band has earned its place in the underground scene. Not without setbacks and challenges ‚Äì but it's exactly that which makes TMM sound harder, rawer, and more convincing than ever.
                Today, 2,700 fans are already following us on Facebook, coming from punk, hardcore, rock, metal, and gothic scenes. This is proof of the versatility and strength of our 'model'. Those who were there know these are not empty words.
                TMM previously played at Ratrock, Sinner's Day, and recently supported Gang of Four at Le Grand Mix (FR). The band features (former) members of Liar, Definitivos, Plan C, Walter Lure (The Heartbreakers) and others.<br><br>
